The paper deals with image denoising and compression, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT), computer vision (cs.CV), multimedia (cs.MM), signal processing (cs.SI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of wavelet transforms is also a common technique in these fields. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
